<div class="title">Peaceful Rolling, Calm Mind, and Total Openness</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Raoul&Exact=1">Raoul</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Raoul. "Peaceful Rolling, Calm Mind, and Total Openness: An Experience with AMT (exp1757)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 12, 2000. erowid.org/exp/1757</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

